<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>[[سورة القارعة <span class="c2">(١٠١)</span> : آية ٩]]<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>فَأُمُّهُ هاوِيَةٌ <span class="c2">(٩)</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>٩-<span class="c5"> فَأُمُّهُ هاوِيَةٌ:</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>فمأواه جهنم، وسميت أما لأنه يأوى إليها.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>[سورة القارعة <span class="c2">(١٠١)</span> : الآيات ١٠ الى ١١]<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>وَما أَدْراكَ ما هِيَهْ <span class="c2">(١٠)</span> نارٌ حامِيَةٌ <span class="c2">(١١)</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>١٠-<span class="c5"> وَما أَدْراكَ ما هِيَهْ:</span><a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>وما أعلمك ما الهاوية.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>١١-<span class="c5"> نارٌ حامِيَةٌ:</span><a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>حامِيَةٌ لا تبلغ حرارتها أية نار.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>